 nd slow roasted\, perfectly seasoned comedic veterans of the NC triangle a
 rea.\n\nLooking forward to laughs and good vibes! Comedy starts at 8pm and
  we’ll meet before it starts and find seats\n\nParking there and the sur
 rounding streets like Broadway Street\, W Corporation Street and North Str
 eet
